commit.message: Recompiled for Java 1.8 and Confluence 5.9.1 with latest Atlassian SDK
UI Integration with User Macros page
Front-end API generalized so that context can be set to 'plugins' (and 'macros' later)
Back-end URLs generalized, not just '/plugins/[key]' but more general, like '/[section]/[key]'. However, security check is still applied so section can be either 'plugins' or 'macros' for now.
Comments added, code refactoring, tooltip auto-update from Collection
Comments added, bug fixed and code refactoring
Comments added, styles grouped by section
Initialization also checks for AJS.dialog2 requirement to be present
Bug fix: allow UTF-8 characters in notes
Compatibility with Confluence 5.5 - 5.8, Universal Plugin Manager 2.15.2 - 2.20.1
Removed GSON dependency from IDEA project
Compatibility with Universal Plugin Manager v.2.20.1
Bug fix: when removing notes, JSON becomes one-liner
